    {
      "id": "66a4a481-e58f-4ce2-b3ec-d92eb56468f5",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $  (E , \\langle   ,  \\rangle )  $ un espace euclidien, $  F  $\net $  G  $ deux sous-espaces vectoriels de $  E  .$ Montrer que~:",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\((E , \\langle   ,  \\rangle )\\)</span> un espace euclidien, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(G\\)</span> deux sous-espaces vectoriels de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(E  .\\)</span> Montrer que :</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0a86e02f-af28-4b15-b75d-51a61cfcf5db",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Si $  F\\subset G  $ alors $  G^\\perp \\subset F^\\perp   .$",
        "html": "<p>Si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F\\subset G\\)</span> alors <span class=\"math inline\">\\(G^\\perp \\subset F^\\perp   .\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "31688661-320f-4d68-9a4a-4a7511977a58",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$  (F+G)^\\perp = F^\\perp \\cap G ^\\perp   .$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((F+G)^\\perp = F^\\perp \\cap G ^\\perp   .\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2e983160-b968-4b70-ad1a-2ba8ad26f168",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$  (F\\cap G)^\\perp = F^\\perp +G ^\\perp   .$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((F\\cap G)^\\perp = F^\\perp +G ^\\perp   .\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c8c146c1-2f4c-4204-800c-67aab29ec629",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Si $\\hbox{dim}(E)  $ est finie, alors $  (F^\\perp )^\\perp =F  .$",
        "html": "<p>Si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\hbox{dim}(E)\\)</span> est finie, alors <span class=\"math inline\">\\((F^\\perp )^\\perp =F  .\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
}